<TITLE>The Infinite Matrix | Rudy Rucker | The Men in the Back Room at the Country Club</TITLE>
<META name="description" content="The Men in the Back Room at the Country Club, a short story by Rudy Rucker, in The Infinite Matrix, a magazine for people who enjoy science fiction as a literature of ideas. Edited by Eileen Gunn.">
